trans-unit.source: Represents information about the functions that may be invoked from the queries written by the Entity SQL query language.
These may be the built-in functions exposed by the storage provider or user-defined functions in a particular database.
Gets the built-in type kind for this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmFunction"></xref>.
One of the enumeration values of the <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind"></xref> enumeration.
Gets a query in the language that is used by the database management system or storage model.
A string value in the syntax used by the database management system or storage model that contains the query or update statement of the <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmFunction"></xref>.
Returns the full name (namespace plus name) of this type.
The full name of the type.
Gets or sets whether this instance is mapped to a function or to a stored procedure.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if this instance is mapped to a function; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if this instance is mapped to a stored procedure.
A collection of type <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection%601> that contains the parameters of this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmFunction"></xref>.
Gets the return parameter of this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmFunction"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.FunctionParameter"></xref> object that represents the return parameter of this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmFunction"></xref>.
Gets the return parameters of this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmFunction"></xref>.
A collection of type <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection%601> that represents the return parameters of this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmFunction"></xref>.
